Detailed Description

Contains the com.rti.dds.domain.DomainParticipant class that acts as an entrypoint of RTI Data Distribution Service and acts as a factory for many of the classes. The com.rti.dds.domain.DomainParticipant also acts as a container for the other objects that make up RTI Data Distribution Service.

"DCPS Domain package"
